## include_form tag

New tag allows you to use normal liquid syntax to pass variables. `render_form` tag is now deprecated.

```liquid
{% raw %}
{% include_form edit_user, id: @user.id %}
{% endraw %}
```

now should be written with

```liquid
{% raw %}
{% include_form 'edit_user', id: user.id %}
{% endraw %}
```

{% include 'alert/warning', content: 'You have to quote form name and you do not include "@" when passing variable.' %}

## log tag

Use log tag to print something to logs.

```liquid
{% raw %}
{% log "hello world" %}
{% log context.params %}
{% log context.params, type: 'error' %}
{% endraw %}
```

{% include 'alert/note', content: 'Default type is info.' %}
